Class FabILContext_c

  • java.lang.Object
    • Context_c

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CodebaseContext, FabILContext

    public class FabILContext_c
extends Context_c
implements FabILContext
    Codebase support for the FabIL typesystem. This class duplicates some of the code in FabricContext_c, but enables FabIL classes to use codebase-relative names.
